1. They will call us at 7.
Will they call us at 7?
They will not call us at 7.
2. They will buy a new flat.
Will they buy a new flat?
They will not buy a new flat.
3. He will bring a little water.
Will he bring a little water?
He will not bring a little water.
4. She will bake a pie.
Will she bake a pie?
She will not bake a pie.
5. Tom will be at home at 3.
Will Tom be at home at 3?
Tom will not be at home at 3.
